Dialogue: Hyah!
Let me show you how it's done.
You lift the hammer like this, then...yah!
Aha...so the secret's to take a running start!
Phew! I need a rest...
We should check on the others' progress.
Sounds like a plan!
Is that blood? Am I bleeding!? Oh, the pain!
Do you require more supplies?
Progress report! And be quick about it!
Are you sure that isn't upside down?
Mustn't forget to take inventory...
Hm? What curious foreign tongue is this?
This should suffice for the time being, Chief.
That scaffold looks awfully wobbly...
Right on schedule, Chief!
Now, what do we need here...?
I'll see that we're all stocked up!
Those are for repairing the rooves. And these...
This stone should serve us well.
Let's see. We still need to stock up on...
Excellent. No delays here.
Now, what tasks remain undone?
My stonemasonry skills will do Ishgard proud!
This, too, would make for a stirring painting...
I'll prepare a copy of the construction schedule for you.
Only the finest materials will do!
Get a hold of yourself, damn it! It's a long way down!
This should serve nicely for the floor.

This is so easy, I could do it with my eyes clo─
OWWW!
You must hone your eye for stone.
Don't forget to haul the materials in the proper order!
The slightest chip or crack could send the walls crashing down.
Yes, this should suffice...
Let me take another look...
I'll do my best!
Aye aye, Chief!
We'll be needing extra hands for this.
Watch out for your hand!
Maybe carpentry isn't for you...
There's no need to rush, you know.
To build a strong foundation, every nail counts...

I think I've finally got the hang of─
OWWW!
A little tap here, and a little tap there...
If only I weren't so clumsy...
How majestic!
Such beautiful stone!
Are you certain we have enough materials?
Your thoroughness is admirable...
I'm prone to mistakes─that's why I always check thrice!
You'll find no better stone in all of Eorzea!
Fifty-one, fifty-two, fifty─wait, did I count that one twice?
If I just stack these here...
This should do!
Oho! Looking good, indeed!
Steady now...
Sigh... Why doesn't she ever notice me?

Watch out for the thumb...watch out for the─
OWWW!
Heh! Lookin' good, eh?
Fastest hammer in Ishgard, I tell you!
Eat up! You'll need all the strength you can muster for the next shift!
Saint Reymanaud's Cathedral wasn't built on an empty stomach, you know.
I'm going to feel this tomorrow...
Time to work off that last flagon of ale!
Unnngaaah!
Nnngraaaaaah!
It's all in the hips...hyaaah!
Right! I'll tell the others.
...And that's what's on the agenda for tomorrow.
Hoooh! Haaah! Hoooh! Haaah!
It just won't break. Am I not doing this right?
Why won't anyone look at me!?
How do you even lift that thing?
Not easily, I'll tell you that...
Let me guess...is it pineapple!?
The chef told me the secret ingredient in the stew...
This shall be the scene for my next masterpiece!
Restoring such a mighty structure will be no small task...!
The smashing's over! It's repairing time!
The damage here is even worse than I thought...
What do I get to smash next!?
Can this truly be restored to its former glory?
You're an inspiration to us all, Chief...
Getting the stairwells just right is tricky, I hear...
There's nothing my muscles can't overcome!
Ngggaaaaaahhh!
Yaaaaaahhh!
It's all in the hips, they say!
Next up is...
Aye, this should serve nicely!
Everything appears in good order...
Isn't it impressive?
Look at the size of this one!
That should do.
Take care not to fall!
You're quite dedicated, aren't you?
A masterpiece shall be wrought...
This is almost fun!
I must do Ishgard proud with my stonework...
Whatever you say, Chief!
All stocked up!
Hm? Did I miscount?
Just like clockwork!
Now where did I leave my hammer?
A solid base if I ever saw one.
Looking good, I'd say.
How goes it?
This is the final push!
Do you know a good chirurgeon? My back is killing me...
That's why I told you to lift with your legs...
Looking better and better!
And that should do it!
Isn't she a beauty?
Ooh! I want to fly in that!
Is it done yet?
I'd say you've earned yourselves a break.
Rest up well, for there's still work to be done!
With a bit more muscle, maybe I'd be better at this...
Your biceps! They cry out in pain!
This wall appears to have escaped the war unscathed...
I'll place an order. How many?
We'll be needing more pickaxes.
Fine material, this!
I must take inventory and report back quickly...
...Ahhhhhh! Working so hard, sometimes I forget to breathe!
A sight to stir the heart and inspire me to the heights of creative genius!
This one's sure to be his magnum opus!
Why, it's lovely!
Best rest up now before the test flight.
Yes, I could use a cup of piping hot tea.
They're gone! Now's our chance!
Kweh! Kweh!♪
Kweh...
Would you sit down?
How can I? I should be out there, cutting down imperials!
It is vital we overcome their advantage in numbers.
An advantage that keeps growing. Xeven's men were hit especially hard.
The enemy could launch a surprise attack at any moment, so be prepared!
You'd be better off heading back to the infirmary and having that leg looked at.
But I can still fight!
Most flattering... Ahem! For the sultana, that is.
Would that I could stay longer, but duty beckons...
I remember it as though it were yesterday.
I fear the time has come for us to depart.
Does Philestiaux have any new tasks that need doing?
Perhaps there are supplies that need procuring.
No good work ever got done on an empty stomach!
I'd like nothing more than to go on a grand adventure!
I've decided to return to Limsa. My beloved may be lost forever, but at least there I have memories...
Look, we can use this stepladder!
Hey, wait for me!
W-Watch out!
Are you sure this will suffice?
Be sure to keep the inventory up to date.
You really have a way with that chisel, don't you?
Hey, I'm no slouch myself!
Heh! You're too kind, miss...
This should do, Chief!
One stone on top of the next...
Leave it to me, Chief!
The stairwell must be finished with all speed!
One step at a time─Featherfall won't be built in a day!
Good as done, Chief!
This wall seems no worse for the wear...
Cut, lay, fit, and repeat...
Building a curved arch of stone is no small task!
Perfection is ever elusive, but I am rather pleased with how this place turned out.
I'll study well, Chief!
This magnificent window frame deserves only the finest glass...!
Ishgardian architecture is truly the pride of the realm!
The inclination of the slope is just as the chief calculated!
Preposterous! Or is it...?
They say the savior of Ishgard <If(PlayerParameter(4))>herself<Else/>himself</If> labors among us!
How is it staying in the Hoarfrost?
Why, I've never lived in such comfort!
Oh, I've forgotten something again!
Shhh! I'm trying to hide here!
Where haven't I looked...?
The captain runs a tight ship, to say the least...
The freshest catches of the day, and exotic spices to season them! We have all you need!
What shall we order from Maisenta?
Mayhap some nuts and other fruits of the forest?
By the Twelve, it's cold here! I can scarce feel my fingertips!
Do any of our fine products catch your discerning eye?
Good work, men!
Get some rest! The next stage will be a demanding one.
Here's to a job well done!
I could swear my biceps are bigger...
My muscles haven't failed me yet!
I knew I could count on you!
Phew! That was the toughest job yet...
My masterpiece is complete!
Hey! What are you doing in there!?
Get down at once─it's dangerous up there!
Manacutter, full speed ahead! Whee!
The adults are back! Let's get out of here!
I'm sorry, mister!
Practice the motion until it becomes second nature!
Don't ask me! I don't know!
You're always alone. Is something the matter?
I lost my husband in the war...
If there's anything I can do for you, just say the word!
You're too kind...
What in the─!? Noooooo!
So this is the new branch of the manufactory...
I can't wait to get to work!
He's truly outdone himself this time.
Ishgard's not so bad...once you get used to the cold.
At least we won't lack for company.
Leave the cooking to me!
And the manufactory's just a hop, skip, and jump away!
It's the savior of Ishgard! In the flesh! Can I shake your hand?
This is sure to win her heart!
This should do it!
The auger's store of aether is running low...
The beaches are safe, for now... Let's hope that shark stays in the water where it belongs.
If any mean old sharks come ashore, Khloe will scare them away! Don't worry, Zhloe!
Oh, you're Zhloe's personal hero!
Now, let's go play on the beach!
The emissaries never give up...
And neither will I!
You know, I'd love to perform here.
I could sing for my friends and family...

I'll talk to the seneschal.
He wouldn't dare say no!
It's always so colorful!
Did you see the costumes?

For the Songbirds?
Yes! Lisette did a fine job!
Tra la la la la.♪
Do doo da doo.♪
La di da dah.♪
Look! It's the Songbirds!
Gosh, they're gorgeous!
Shall we watch for a while?
I suppose we should go...
That was so much fun!
It certainly was!
I feel so close to Ulala!
Now that you mention it...
They do seem alike, kupo!
Ulala! Over here!
Narumi! My queen!
Masha, I love you!
I adore your outfits!
The Songbirds are life!
I wish we could talk to Elyne again.
And Kupka, too!
Just a little more rest, then I can see the Songbirds!
It's all so pretty!
I wanted to help decorate...
Oh my...
Where... \\<pant> \\<pant> could she have gone?
Which do you prefer, my dear?
Oh, the one with the ribbon is just lovely!
Stay focused, now.
Don't show any fear─they can smell it!
Quite a fight she put up...
Blood! Blood! Blood!
One of you should take responsibility!
Hurry up and punish somebody already.
I'm so tired of this.
I can't relax until we hang someone out to dry.
I haven't done anything...that you can prove.
I haven't slept in a week!
Or twenty! Haha... Please help me.
Should have all the parts you need here.
The workshop seems so...peaceful.
Busy time?
Seems like you could use a hand.
Perfect. I'll have a look.
Take a break! Relax!
I can't believe we're working with Neillemard!
More importantly, Nimie. Her eyes are so piercing... \\<sigh>
True, but Denys is the gorgeous one...
Wait, how long have we been out here?
I could not have asked for a better present than spending the Starlight season with you!
It's a miracle I was granted a respite from my duties.
Is it just me, or do things look particularly festive this year?
We couldn't have done it without you.
See those decorations? They were all mine!
They're beautiful! You truly have an eye for these things...
We've got some new faces joining us today!
Great! We could use the help!
Rookies to boss around? All right!
I'm with you, Chief!
I'll put some muscle on you!
Pray disregard my station. I will perform any task, and gladly.
Hyah!
Can't help but feel I'm a bit rusty after all that time off...
This thing is heavier than it looks...
Ho!
This city has so many more faces I must capture on canvas...
Right back in the swing of things─just as I like to see it.
Have you ever lifted a pickaxe in your life?
Good to be back on the job, Chief!
I fear this is my first foray into manual labor...
Let an expert show you how it's done!
I thank you for your wisdom, my friend.
You have potential, I'll say that much.
Have to provide a good example for the newcomers!
Yes, it's coming back to me now! It's all in the hips...
Eyaaahhh!
It's as hard as a... Well, I guess it is a rock.
All right! Which one of you dumped this rubbish here!?
Now, now... Let's take a deep breath...
How am I supposed to read these chocobo scratches!?
Are you not, perchance, holding that backwards?
Sixteen? Are you sure it wasn't eighteen?
When in doubt, it never hurts to consult the skybuilders' board.
This is a vital task! Our inventory's not going to count itself.
Hey you! Up there! Don't forget to show the rookies how it's done!
Keeping inventory may not be a glamorous task, but it's a necessary one.
Leave it to me, Chief!
Consider it done, milo─er, Lord Chief.
We've got materials in spades, but we could use a few more hands.
Just leave it to me.
Let's see what else needs doing...
I'll prepare it at once!
I'd best place a new order before we run out of supplies...
Report to me as soon as your task is done, you hear?
Got it, Miss!
How many times must I tell you to keep your eye on the nail!?
Must keep focus... Must keep focus...
Allow me to show you how it's─owww!
Oh, dear... That couldn't have felt good...
A tappity-tap here, a tappity-tap there...
Am I doing this right?
Looking good! Keep it up!
I don't want to see a single bent nail! Understood?
How's this, Chief?
Looking rather sharp, if I do say so myself! Haha!
Consider it done, Lord─er, Chief.
The masses may not appreciate it, but this will be my greatest masterpiece yet!
Numbers aren't your strong suit, are they?
Better safe than sorry...
Seventy-one, seventy-two, seventy-four... Wait, where was I again?
Pray forgive my impropriety, but mayhap you forgot seventy-three...?
Sounds good to me!
We have enough supplies here, yes?
Shall I bring more from our reserves?
Always good to see my skybuilders get into their work!
Don't forget to rest up from time to time. We've a long way to go.
I learned it all from you, Chief!
Now that's a generous donation! We'll put it to good use!
You are far too kind, Chief...
I said, watch out!
Have to set a good example for the newcomers...!
It's all in the─ow! Okay, now that was an example of what not to do.
Shall I summon a healer?
At this rate, I'm going to run out of nails...
One task done, now it's on to the next...
Your technique's improved, I see.
I reckon you're a natural at this.
Tap, tap, tappity-tap!
This may very well be my best work yet!
You flatter me overmuch, Chief...
Don't look down. Don't look down. Don't look─damn it all!
Just like that, now. Take it nice and easy.
Truth be told, I enjoy working in silence.
You'll want to climb up to make sure everything is in place.
I can see I still have much to learn from my seniors...
Now you're talking. I'm famished!
Shall we take a short respite?
Your stamina has improved greatly. Consider me impressed.
Always remember: endurance is as important as technique─if not more so.
Thanks, Chief! I've trained hard for this day!
I'd best take another look at the plans...
Endurance indeed. I thank you for your wisdom, Chief.
Be careful now, will you!?
I've never seen wood of such quality!
I've got it down this time, I swear. Just watch me n─owww!
How did I know that was going to happen...?
Bam! Bam! Bam!
I wouldn't mind living in a house like this myself!
Keep it up, and you'll need my supervision no longer.
Don't get ahead of yourself, now. One nail at a time.
Heh! I could never have done it without you, Chief!
Could it be? Are we ahead of schedule?
I will endeavor to do just that, milo─er, Chief.
Develop an eye for quality materials, and it will serve you well.
Just need to smooth and polish, now...
I've developed quite the discerning eye, if I do say so myself...
Do we have all we need?
'Tis an honor to serve, Chief.
You've quite an aptitude for art, I'd say.
I reckon I'm even more talented with a chisel than with a hammer!
I mean not to boast, but I have trained some in artistic pursuits.
Consider it done!
Here it is! You know where it all goes. Thank you kindly!
Well? What do you think?
Remember: the final inspection's nigh as important as the job itself.
This won't hold in its current state. Better to reinforce it further.
Not a crack or blemish to speak of!
That should do it! Now, to take one final look...
As you command, Chief.
You require a demonstration, you say? Very well, then...
The key is to put your whole body into it. Now behold! Hyaaaaaaaaah!
You'll get the hang of it in no time.
What in the hells is this made of? My axe's scarcely even scratching it!
If only the chief would give me a private lesson, too...
Such power!
The student has become a teacher. What a marvelous sight!
This task is mine─and mine alone!
It's all in the hips, you see?
'Tis not nearly so simple as it looks. Your wisdom is invaluable.
How did it go again? The chief makes it look so easy...
For the Firmament! For the chief! For our future!
You've come a long way, haven't you?
She'll notice me sooner or later─I just know it!
That's the way!
He-YAH!
Is my work satisfactory?
Mark my words: you will break before me. Hah!
Ngggh... Yah!
To think the reconstruction effort is almost at an end... Such a bittersweet feeling, it is.
Well, look who's showing the rookies the ropes now!
I still remember the day he first joined up. He's like a whole new man!
Worry not─I'll show you how it's done!
You are truly a generous teacher, my friend.
Don't overdo it. Injure yourself, and you'll be no use to anyone.
You've got a knack for numbers. We've sorely needed someone like you.
This is quality stone, Chief! I can vouch for it!
I can't shake the feeling that we're running low...
I've done the calculations, and I do believe we have sufficient quantities of everything.
I just finished my count─I guarantee you I overlooked nothing!
Thanks to you, I've neither a dearth nor a surplus of supplies!
That's the last task on my list. I'd best check back at the skybuilders' board.
Aha...duly noted.
Everything seems to be in good order here.
Yes, this! This shall be my magnum opus!
Oho! I can scarcely wait to see the finished work!
Is there no limit to this man's talent and passion!?
Why, it is as if the city comes to life on his canvas!
Are my eyes to be believed?
Practice makes perfect, after all!
My fingers don't sting for once! Amazing!
Pray teach me to wield the hammer with such skill.
Excellent. Make sure to teach the others.
Looking good. Carry on, carry on...
Precision and speed. Both are essential...
Where'd the chief go...?
Might I trouble you to inspect my work, Chief?
Hyah! Hyah!
But of course! I'll be finished here any moment...
We have another task for you...
Look at how he's grown...
Generous souls went out of their way to gather these materials for us. We must make the most of them.
Remember, quantity means nothing without quality!
I am indebted to you for your wisdom.
I can scarce feel my hands!
Have we finished, then...?
She's twitching... Is that normal?
Nothing quite like a kiln-fresh familiar.
I never knew familiar-creation could be so rough...
Do you reckon these are dry yet?
Welcome to the Firmament, my dear madam! What brings you to these heavenly environs today?
I make for the Abacus. They say some most exquisite silks from the Far East have arrived!
How splendid! Might I have the honor of escorting you there?
You are far too kind, my good ser. 'Twould be a pleasure.
Fine furs and hides to shelter your skin from the bitter cold!
Have anythin' what needs fixin'? I'm your man!
I've never seen anything quite like it...
Say no more, my good man! I have everything you need...
Do you perchance have needles and thread in supply? I mean to learn weaving...
Mayhap I, too, will write my memoirs one day...
Ow! I want to find whoever dropped that kupo nut on the street and slap them silly!
To soak a bit longer or head for the steam baths? That is the question...
What a breathtaking sight...!
A studio befitting my prodigious talents!
My masterpieces will surely fetch good coin in Featherfall...
I will stop at nothing to see the Firmament safe for residents and visitors alike!
All right, time to make the rounds again...
This is our new home! Isn't it lovely?
How warm and toasty it must be inside!
How long does she mean to keep me waiting...?
I bought some fine wine from a distant land. What say we raise a toast?
Beg pardon, but what are you doing in front of our house?
Finally, my dear sister and I have a home of our own!
Let's go inside. We'll catch our death of cold out here.
The child will meet us here, they say?
So I was told. Let us give her the warmest of welcomes.
W-Welcome, child─er, my daughter.
Forgive your father, my dear. He can be terribly stiff on these occasions.
Father! Mother! How happy I am to be part of your family!
Well, doesn't your coat look so warm and toasty!
Baaaaaa! Baaaaaa!
And what a fine nest this is!
Thanks to Ehll Tou, we're now allowed to live here, too!
My back aches just looking at her...
It's all in the hips!
Well, look who's come to visit!
Might I join you, kupo?
'Tis my duty to see that all the instruments are tuned to perfection.
What a magnificent structure! Whatever do you suppose it's for?
They say it's to serve as lodgings for luminaries and guests of honor.
No entry allowed. The interior is still undergoing renovations.
But that's all the coin I have...
The other vendors may not be open for business yet, but we certainly are!
